OL,4,CReport says job centres failing long
OL,5,Cterm sick
OL,7,FA new report has said Job Centres are
OL,8,Ffailing to help the long-term sick, a
OL,9,Fsection of society the government is
OL,10,Fkeen to get back into work, ITV News
OL,11,FBusiness Editor Joel Hills reports
OL,13,FOnce upon a time, Barnsley struggled
OL,14,Fas the collieries closed.
OL,16,FToday, the town's problem isn't
OL,17,Funemployment, it's economic inactivity.
OL,19,FAnd Barnsley isn't alone.
