OL,7,FIn Barnsley Library, I met Tammy
OL,8,FHighley who is off benefits and is on
OL,9,Fthe road back into employment.
OL,11,FShe has had to study but three years
OL,12,Fafter a series of illnesses -
OL,13,Fincluding a pulmonary embolism,
OL,14,Fthyroid problems and a hernia - and
OL,15,Fshe is due to start training as a
OL,16,Fteaching assistant in September.
OL,18,FThis is her victory but she insists it
OL,19,Fwas a team effort.
