OL,7,F"At Adastra (a local community
OL,8,Fcompany), Michelle and Rachel they've
OL,9,Fhelped me amazingly," she said.
OL,11,F"As well as the other ladies I've met
OL,12,Fin Women's Group, there's Kelly who is
OL,13,Fmy employment and information advisor
OL,14,Fat Barnsley Council."
OL,16,FThe support was vital. Without it,
OL,17,FTammy says she would be "stuck at
OL,18,Fhome, depressed and miserable".
OL,20,FBarnsley's Job Centre Plus does not
OL,21,Fmake Tammy's list of thanks.
