OL,7,FThe council set up the Pathways to
OL,8,FWork Commission to assess how best to
OL,9,Ftackle economic inactivity, in
OL,10,FBarnsley and across the UK.
OL,12,FThe study was led by the former Labour
OL,13,Fminister Alan Milburn and concludes
OL,14,Fthat the benefits, health and
OL,15,Femployment system are "failing
OL,16,Fcatastrophically".
