OL,7,F"The whole system is dysfunctional,"
OL,8,FMilburn told ITV News. "At the moment,
OL,9,Fit's just a chaotic mess of so many
OL,10,Finitiatives, so many programmes.
OL,11,FNobody can navigate it. And unless we
OL,12,Fcan get that right, the incentives for
OL,13,Fpeople who might want to work to
OL,14,Factually actively seek employment."
OL,16,FThe number of people who are
OL,17,F"economically inactive" due to long-
OL,18,Fterm sickness has risen by more than
OL,19,F700,000 in the last four years,
OL,20,Faccording to the Office of National
OL,21,FStatistics.
