OL,7,FThe Milburn Commission's report says
OL,8,Fthat seven in ten people who are
OL,9,Fcurrently not working or looking for
OL,10,Fwork would take a job if it "aligned
OL,11,Fwith their skills, interests and
OL,12,Fcircumstances".
OL,14,FIt makes a series of recommendations
OL,15,Fwhich it argues could help as many as
OL,16,Fthree million people to return to the
OL,17,Fworkforce.
