OL,7,FJob centres should be radically
OL,8,Freformed to become a one-stop shop for
OL,9,Fall support services - integrating
OL,10,Fthem with health services to better
OL,11,Fsupport the long-term sick.
OL,13,FIt recommends a devolution of power to
OL,14,Fcouncils and regional mayors to ensure.
OL,16,FThe new government is set to adopt
OL,17,Fboth of these ideas.
