OL,7,FThe report argues this gap is
OL,8,F"perverse" and that, as a result, "it
OL,9,Fpays to be classified as incapable of
OL,10,Fwork rather than actively seeking it".
OL,12,FWill the new minister change benefits
OL,13,Fpayments?
OL,15,FLiz Kendall won't say. She was in
OL,16,FBarnsley today to welcome the report
OL,17,Fand to promise reform.
OL,19,FThe increase in the number of people
OL,20,Fclaiming incapacity and disability
OL,21,Fbenefits is a worrying trend.
